217
00:12:15,937 --> 00:12:16,837
She's been alone

218
00:12:17,839 --> 00:12:18,772
since she was young

219
00:12:19,507 --> 00:12:20,774
and now she's wandering outside

220
00:12:22,477 --> 00:12:23,377
Her path ahead

221
00:12:24,612 --> 00:12:25,579
