230
00:12:53,274 --> 00:12:54,174
On the ninth day of the ninth month

231
00:12:54,776 --> 00:12:55,742
I was found in swaddling clothes

232
00:12:55,977 --> 00:12:57,511
taken in by an old woman in the mountains

233
00:12:58,780 --> 00:12:59,780
My foster mother

234
00:13:00,214 --> 00:13:02,382
fell seriously ill when I was young

235
00:13:03,217 --> 00:13:05,152
So I had to learn medical skills on my own

236
00:13:07,689 --> 00:13:09,389
But in the end, I was still helpless

237
00:13:16,230 --> 00:13:18,298
You must have been very lonely

238
00:13:19,667 --> 00:13:21,702
We spirits may not have parents

239
00:13:22,170 --> 00:13:24,304
but ever since I was young, I was incomplete

240
00:13:25,340 --> 00:13:27,607
Eyes, ears, nose, body, mind, and intentions

241
00:13:28,810 --> 00:13:30,110
