255
00:14:34,375 --> 00:14:35,609
How beautiful

256
00:14:36,477 --> 00:14:37,310
Are you

257
00:14:39,080 --> 00:14:40,180
still hungry?

258
00:15:17,018 --> 00:15:18,652
Such a powerful spirit

259
00:15:18,953 --> 00:15:20,187
Truly unheard of

260
00:15:20,788 --> 00:15:22,022
With her spirit alone

261
00:15:22,290 --> 00:15:23,824
